n successfully deleted.'=>'Item menu iki wis kasil dibusak.','enter a custom date format in the following field'=>'lebokaké format tanggal racikan nang ros ngisor iki','enter a custom time format in the following field'=>'lebokaké format wektu racikan nang ros ngisor iki','revision date short formatj M @ H:i'=>'j M @ H:i','The %s constant in your %s file is no longer needed.'=>'Konstanta %s nang berkas %s Sampéyan wis ora diperlokaké manèh.','%d star'=>'%d bintang' . "\0" . '%d bintang-bintang','WordPress %1$s running %2$s theme.'=>'WordPress %1$s njalanaké tema %2$s.','If you have marked plugins as favorites on WordPress.org, you can browse them here.'=>'Yèn sampéyan nandhani plugin iki dadi favorit nang WordPress.org, sampéyan bisa nlusuri nang kéné.','<strong>ERROR</strong>: Please enter a nickname.'=>'<strong>SULAYA</strong>: Mānggā ngleboknā Jeneng panganggo.','Remember, once deleted your site cannot be restored.'=>'Èlingānā, sepisanan dibusak situs Sampéyan ora bisā dibalèkaké.','Failed to repair the %1$s table. Error: %2$s'=>'Gagal mbeneri tabel %1$s. Kaluputan: %2$s','Welcome to WordPress %1$s. <a href="%2$s">Learn more</a>.'=>'Sugeng Rawuh marang WordPress %1$s. <a href="%2$s">Sinau Lenggkapé</a>.','Failed to optimize the %1$s table. Error: %2$s'=>'Gagal ngoptimasi tabel %1$s table. Kaluputan: %2$s','<strong>ERROR</strong>: options page not found.'=>'<strong>KALUPUTAN</strong>: opsi kācā ora ditemokaké.','There are some invalid menu items. Please check or delete them.'=>'Ānā saperangan item menu sing keliru. Priksāni utāwā dibusak mawon.','The boxes on your Dashboard screen are:'=>'Kothakan nang layar Dasbor yaiku:','You must provide a valid email address.'=>'Sampéyan kudu ngleboknā alamat e-mail sing valid.','Please enter a valid menu name.'=>'Mānggā ngleboknā jeneng racikan sing valid.','Executed before Multisite is loaded.'=>'Dilakoknā sakdurunge Multi Situs dimuat.','Enter new'=>'Ngleboknā Anyar','You did not enter a category name.'=>'Sampéyan ora ngle