###SITE_NAME###','One or more database tables are unavailable. To allow WordPress to attempt to repair these tables, press the &#8220;Repair Database&#8221; button. Repairing can take a while, so please be patient.'=>'Salah siji utāwā luwih tabel database ora cumawis. Kanggo ngidinaké WordPress ngupāyā ndandani tabel-tabel iki, pencèt tombol &#8220;Ndandani Database&#8221; Ndandaniné bisa mangan wektu, mānggā nunggu sing sabar mawon.','There is a new version of %1$s available. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>View version %4$s details</a>. <em>Automatic update is unavailable for this plugin.</em>'=>'Ānā versi anyar sākā %1$s wis cumawis. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>Tonton detil versi %4$s</a>. <em>Update otomatis wis cumawis kanggo plugin iki.</em>','These suggestions are based on the plugins you and other users have installed.'=>'Saran iki adhedasar sākā plugin Sampéyan lan panganggo liyané sing uwis tau masang.','This screen allows you to edit five fields for metadata in a file within the media library.'=>'Laman iki ngidinaké sampéyan kanggo nyunting limang ros metadata nang berkas sing ānā nang pustaka media.','To add a custom link, <strong>expand the Custom Links section, enter a URL and link text, and click Add to Menu</strong>'=>'Kanggo nambah pranālā racikan, <strong>megaraké seksi Pranālā Racikan, lebokaké URL lan teks tautan, lan klik Tambah nang Menu</strong>','Usernames can have only alphanumeric characters, spaces, underscores, hyphens, periods, and the @ symbol.'=>'Jeneng panganggo namung bisā diisi abjad, angka, spasi, garis ngisor, tandha hubung, tandha petik lan simbol @.','You are currently editing the page that shows your latest posts.'=>'Sampéyan saiki nyunting kācā sing nontonaké kiriman pungkasan Sampéyan.','You are using a development version of WordPress. These feature plugins are also under development. <a href="%s">Learn more</a>.'=>'Sampéyan nganggo versi pengembangan WordPress. Fitur plugin iki ugā ésih pangembangan.  <a href="%s">Nyinauni lengkapé</a>.','You can set the language, and the translation files will be automatically downloaded and installed (available if your filesystem is writable).'=>'Sampéyan bisā nyetèl bāsā, lan berkas terjemahan bakal otomatis diundhuh lan dipasang (bisā cumawis yèn sistim berkasé bisā ditulisi).','You&rsquo;re using the auto-generated password for your account. Would you like to change it?'=>'Sampéyan nganggo kode sandhi otomatis nang akun Sampéyan . Sampéyan kepéngin ngganti?','Could not fully remove the plugin %s.'=>'Ora bisā mbuang plugin %s kanthi tuntas.','I understand'=>'Aku ngerti','Heads up!'=>'Unggahaké!','<strong>Warning:</strong> Making changes to active plugins is not recommended.'=>'<strong>Welingan:</strong> Gawé owahan nang plugin sing aktif ora dianjuraké.','Selected file content:'=>'Berkas konten sing dipilih:','There was an error while trying to update the file. You may need to fix something and try updating again.'=>'Ānā kaluputan nalikā nyoba ngupdate berkas iki. Sampéyan kudu ndandani āpā sing perlu lan coba diupdaté manéh.','Homepage: %s'=>'Kācā utāma: %s','Available tags:'=>'Tetenger sing cumawis:','%s (A sanitized version of the author name.)'=>'%s (Versi resik sākā jeneng penulis.)','%s (The sanitized post title (slug).)'=>'%s (Judhul pos sing resik (slug).)','%s (The unique ID of the post, for example 423.)'=>'%s (ID unik pos, contoné 423.)','%s (Second of the minute, for example 33.)'=>'%s (Detik semenit, contoné 33.)','%s (Minute of the hour, for example 43.)'=>'%s (Menit sejam, contoné 43.)','%s (Hour of the day, for example 15.)'=>'%s (Jam sedina, contoné 15.)','%s (Day of the month, for example 28.)'=>'%s (Din seminggo, contoné 28.)','%s (Month of the year, for example 05.)'=>'%s (Wulan setahun, contoné 05.)','%s (The year of the post, four digits, for example 2004.)'=>'%s (Tahun kiriman, patang digit, contoné 2004.)','Theme Installation'=>'Instalasi Tema','%s is already editing this post.'=>'%s uwis nyunting tulisan iki.','%s is already editing this post. Do you want to take over?'=>'%s uwis nyunting pos iki. Sampéyan péngin ngganténi?','<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Sites_Screen">Documentation on Site Management</a>'=>'<a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Network_Admin_Sites_Screen">Dokumentasi babagan Manajemen Situs</a>','Plugin Installation'=>'Instalasi plugin','Custom installation script.'=>'Skrip instalasi racikan.','Active Installations:'=>'Instalasi aktif:','<strong>Info</strong> &mdash; The site URL is rarely edited as this can cause the site to not work properly. The Registered date and Last Updated date are displayed. Network admins can mark a site as archived, spam, deleted and mature, to remove from public listings or disable.'=>'<strong>Info</strong> &mdash; URL situs iku arang disunting amargā bisā nyebabaké situsé ora bisa mlaku. Tanggal pendaftaran lan pungkasan ngupdate ugā ditampilaké. Admin jaringan bisa nandhani situs dadi arsip, spam, dibusak lan dewasa, kanggo ngilangi sākā sawangan umum utāwā dipaténi.','<strong>Settings</strong> &mdash; This page shows a list of all settings associated with this site. Some are created by WordPress and others are created by plugins you activate. Note that some fields are grayed out and say Serialized Data. You cannot modify these values due to the way the setting is stored in the database.'=>'<strong>Settings</strong> &mdash; Kācā iki nampilaké kabèh setèlan sing ānā sangkutané karo situs iki. Sapérangan digawé nganggo WordPress lan liyané digawé karo plugin sing diaktifaké. Kālā-kālā sapérangan ros kuwi kabur lan ngetokaké Runtutan Data. Sampéyan ora bisā ngowahi biji-bijiné saknajan setélan iki disimpen nang database.','<strong>Themes</strong> &mdash; This area shows themes that are not already enabled across the network. Enabling a theme in this menu makes it accessible to this site. It does not activate the theme, but allows it to show in the site&#8217;s Appearance menu. To enable a theme for the entire network, see the <a href="%s">Network Themes</a> screen.'=>'<strong>Tema</strong> &mdash; Area iki nontonaké tema-tema sing durung siap diuripaké nang sebrang jaringan. Nguripaké tema nang menu iki ndadékaké bisa diakses kanggo situs iki. Iki ora ngaktifaké tema, nanging ingidinaké kanggo ditonton sakjroné menu Pakeliran situs. Kanggo nguripaké tema nang sakjroning jaringan, wacanānā laman <a href="%s">Tema Jaringan</a>.','(%s ratings)'=>'(%s peringkat)','Hi, this is a comment.
To get started with moderating, editing, and deleting comments, please visit the Comments screen in the dashboard.
Commenter avatars come from <a href="https://gravatar.com">Gravatar</a>.'=>'Hai, iki kuwi komentar.
Kanggo miwiti moderasi, nyunting lan mbusak komentar-komentar mānggā nuju marang laman Komentar nang dasbor.
Avatar penulis komentar dijupuk sākā <a href="https://gravatar.com">Gravatar</a>.','This will replace the current editor content with the last backup version. You can use undo and redo in the editor to get the old content back or to return to the restored version.'=>'Iki ngganténi penyunting konten karo versi backup pungkasan. Sampéyan bisa maju lan munduraké kasil ketikan nang editor kanggo kanggo mbalekaké konten lawas utāwā mbalik nang versi simpenané.','Your theme supports %s menu. Select which menu appears in each location.'=>'Tema Sampéyan nyokong menu %s . Pilihānā menu endi sing ditontonaké nang saben lokasi.' . "\0" . 'Tema Sampéyan nyokong menu-menu %s . Pilihānā menu endi sing ditontonaké nang saben lokasi.','<strong>At A Glance</strong> &mdash; Displays a summary of the content on your site and identifies which theme and version of WordPress you are using.'=>'<strong>Sekapur Sirih</strong> &mdash; Nampilaké ringkesan sākā konten nang situs Sampéyan lan ngenali tema endi lan versi WordPress sing Sampéyan gunaknā.','<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/forum/multisite/">Support Forums</a>'=>'<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/forum/multisite/">Forum Panyokong</a>','%1$s rating based on %2$s rating'=>'peringkat %1$s adedhasar peringkat %2$s' . "\0" . 'peringkat %1$s adedhasar peringkat-peringkat %2$s','This screen shows an individual user all of their sites in this network, and also allows that user to set a primary site. They can use the links under each site to visit either the front end or the dashboard for that site.'=>'Layar iki nontonaké saben panganggo nang sakabehing situs nang jaringan iki, lan ugā ngidinaké panganggo nyetél situs utamané. Dhéwéké bisā nganggo pranālā nang ngisor situs kanggo niliki salah siji kācā ngarep utāwā dasbor situs iku.','<strong>Activity</strong> &mdash; Shows the upcoming scheduled posts, recently published posts, and the most recent comments on your posts and allows you to moderate them.'=>'<strong>Aktifitas</strong> &mdash; Nontonaké jadwal pos sing arep dikirim, pos sing paling anyar dipacak, lan komentar paling anyar nang pos sampéyan lan ngidinaké sampéyan kanggo moderasiné.','<strong>Screen Options</strong> &mdash; Use the Screen Options tab to choose which Dashboard boxes to show.'=>'<strong>Opsi Layar</strong> &mdash; Nganggoā tab Opsi Layar kanggo milih kothak dasbor endi sing ditontonaké.','There is not enough free disk space to complete the update.'=>'Ora cukup kapasitas disk kanggo njangkepi update.','Sorry, that isn&#8217;t a valid email address. Email addresses look like <code>username@example.com</code>.'=>'Pangapurané, kuwi ketoké dudu alamat email sing bener. Alamat email kuduné kaāyā <code>panganggo@tuladha.com</code>.','Your passwords do not match. Please try again.'=>'Sandhi Sampéyan ora cocog. Mānggā dicoba malih.','The username you provided has invalid characters.'=>'Jeneng panganggo sing Sampéyan tulisnā nduwéni karakter sing keliru.','Sorry, something went wrong. The requested comparison could not be loaded.'=>'Pangapurané, ānā kedadèn kaluputan. Panjalukan perbandingan ora bisā diamot.','Add menu items from the column on the left.'=>'Tambah item menu sākā kolom nang sebelah kiwā.','Drag each item into the order you prefer. Click the arrow on the right of the item to reveal additional configuration options.'=>'Gérèd saben item marang urutan sing Sampéyan penginaké. Klik panah nang sebelah tengen item kanggo ngetokaké opsi pengaturan tambahan.','If you haven&#8217;t yet created any menus, <strong>click the &#8217;create a new menu&#8217; link</strong> to get started'=>'Yèn Sampéyan durung gawé sembarang menu, <strong>klik pranālā gawé menu anyar</strong> kanggo miwiti','To edit a menu currently assigned to a theme location, <strong>click the adjacent &#8217;Edit&#8217; link</strong>'=>'Kanggo nyunting menu saiki mlebu marang panggonan tema, <strong>klik pranālā Sunting</strong>','To assign menus to one or more theme locations, <strong>select a menu from each location&#8217;s drop down.</strong> When you&#8217;re finished, <strong>click Save Changes</strong>'=>'Kanggo nglebokaké menu marang siji utāwā luwih nang panggonan tema, <strong>pilih menu sākā lokasi menu keréh.</strong> Yèn Sampéyan wis rampung, <strong>klik Simpen Owahan</strong>','This screen is used for globally assigning menus to locations defined by your theme.'=>'Laman iki umum digunakaké kanggo nglebokake menu marang lokasi sing ditentokaké tema.','Delete a menu item by <strong>expanding it and clicking the Remove link</strong>'=>'Mbusak item menu karo <strong>ngembagaké lan ngeklik pranālā Buwang</strong>','Add one or several items at once by <strong>selecting the checkbox next to each item and clicking Add to Menu</strong>'=>'Tambah siji utāwā pirang-pirang item sepisan karo <strong>milih kothak cek terus nganti saben item lan ngeklik Tambah marang Menu</strong>','To edit an existing menu, <strong>choose a menu from the drop down and click Select</strong>'=>'Kanggo nyunting menu sing wis ānā, <strong>pilih menu sākā menu keréh lan klik Pilih</strong>','The menu management box at the top of the screen is used to control which menu is opened in the editor below.'=>'Kothak manajemen menu nang ndhuwur layar digunaknā kanggo ngatur saben menu sing dibukā nang editor ngisor iki.','Add, organize, and modify individual menu items'=>'Tambah, natani, lan ngubah dhéwé-dhéwé item menu','Your latest changes were saved as a revision.'=>'Owahan pungkasan Sampéyan uwis disimpen dadi revisi.','The backup of this post in your browser is different from the version below.'=>'Backup pos iki nang peramban Sampéyan iku bédā karo versi ngisor iki.','Edit your menu below, or <a href="%s">create a new menu</a>.'=>'Sunting menu Sampéyan ngisor iki, utāwā <a href="%s">gawé menu anyar</a>.','Give your menu a name, then click Create Menu.'=>'Wénéhi menu Sampéyan jeneng, terus klik Gawé Menu.','Edit your default menu by adding or removing items. Drag each item into the order you prefer. Click Create Menu to save your changes.'=>'Nyunitng menu gawan Sampéyan karo nambahi utāwā mbusaki item-item. Géréd saben item marang sing dikarepaké. Klik Gawé Menu kanggo nyimpen suntingan Sampéyan.','It is up to search engines to honor this request.'=>'Iki apik kanggo mesin panggolèkan kanggo ngregani panjalukan iki.','Discourage search engines from indexing this site'=>'Ciyutaké mesin panggolékan nganggo pangindekan situs iki','Allow search engines to index this site'=>'Ngidinaké mesin panggolekan kanggo ngindeks situs iki','Welcome to WordPress %1$s. You will be redirected to the About WordPress screen. If not, click <a href="%2$s">here</a>.'=>'Sugeng Rawuh marang WordPress %1$s. Sampéyan arep dialihaké marang laman Ngenani WordPress. Yèn ora, klik <a href="%2$s">kéné</a>.','You attempted to edit an item that isn&#8217;t an attachment. Please go back and try again.'=>'Sampéyan ngupāyā nyunting item sing dudu sampiran. Mānggā mbalik mawon lan diulangi malih.','<strong>Welcome</strong> &mdash; Shows links for some of the most common tasks when setting up a new site.'=>'<strong>Wilujeng</strong> &mdash; Tontonaké pranālā kanggo sapérangan prentah umum nalikā nyetèl situs anyar.','There is a new version of %1$s available. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>View version %4$s details</a>. <em>Automatic update is unavailable for this theme.</em>'=>'Versi anyar sākā %1$s wis cumawis. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>Tonton detil versi %4$s</a>. <em>Update otomatis wis cumawis kanggo tema iki.</em>','Thank you. Please check your email for a link to confirm your action. Your site will not be deleted until this link is clicked.'=>'Matur nuwun. Mānggā dicek email Sampéyan sing ānā pranālāné kanggo ngonfirmasi aksi Sampéyan. Situs Sampéyan ora dibusak nganti pranālā iki dibusak.','Thank you for using %s, your site has been deleted. Happy trails to you until we meet again.'=>'Matur nuwun uwis nganggo %s, situs Sampéyan uwis dibusak. Mugi rahayu lan Sugeng kepanggihan malih.','Sorry, the link you clicked is stale. Please select another option.'=>'Pangapurané, pranālā sing Sampéyan klik uwis kadaluwarsa. Mānggā milih opsi liyané.','I\'m sure I want to permanently disable my site, and I am aware I can never get it back or use %s again.'=>'Aku yakin Aku péngin mbusak selawasé situsku, lan aku ora peduli arep njupuk lan nganggo %s manéh.','There is a new version of %1$s available. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>View version %4$s details</a> or <a href="%5$s" %6$s>update now</a>.'=>'Versi anyar sākā %1$s uwis cumawis. <a href="%2$s" %3$s>Nonton detil versi %4$s</a> or <a href="%5$s" %6$s>update saiki</a>.','To allow use of this page to automatically repair database problems, please add the following line to your %s file. Once this line is added to your config, reload this page.'=>'Kanggo ngidinaké kācā iki otomatis ndandani masalah database, mānggā tambahi baris ngisor iki marang berkas %s Sampéyan. Sepisan baris iki ditambahaké marang config, terus diamot ulang kācā iki.','WordPress can automatically look for some common database problems and repair them. Repairing can take a while, so please be patient.'=>'WordPress bisā otomatis nemoni sapérangan masalah dasar database lan bisā ndandani. Ndandani iku bisā mbutuhaké wektu, māngga nunggu sing sabar.','Repairs complete. Please remove the following line from wp-config.php to prevent this page from being used by unauthorized users.'=>'Wis rampung ndandani. Mānggā buwangi baris iki sākā wp-config.php kanggo njagani kācā iki digunaknā nang panganggo sing ora resmi.','The %1$s table is not okay. It is reporting the following error: %2$s. WordPress will attempt to repair this table&hellip;'=>'Tabel %1$s ora bérès. Ānā laporan kaluputan iki: %2$s. WordPress ngupayāaké ndandani tabel&hellip; iki;','Uploading Files allows you to choose the folder and path for storing your uploaded files.'=>'Ngunggah berkas-berkas ngidinaké Sampéyan kanggo milih folder lan path kanggo nyimpenberkas unggahan.','If desired, WordPress will automatically alert various services of your new posts.'=>'Yén gelem, WordPress bakal otomatis ngélingaké layanan-layanan nang pos anyar Sampéyan.','<strong>Drag and drop</strong> your files into the area below. Multiple files are allowed.'=>'<strong>Gered lan Tibaknā</strong> berkas sampéyan marang area ngisor iki. Ngunggah berkas bebarengan ugā diidinaké.','Links may be separated into Link Categories; these are different than the categories used on your posts.'=>'Pranālā mungkin kepisah sākā Kategori Pranālā; iki bedā karo kategori sing Sampéyan enggo nang pos sampéyan.','You can use the following controls to arrange your Dashboard screen to suit your workflow. This is true on most other administration screens as well.'=>'Sampéyan bisa nganggo kontrol ngisor iki kanggo natani layar Dasbor kanggo ngapiki kerjā Sampéyan. Iki ugā bisā mlaku nang layar administrasi liyané kanthi lancar.','Note: Neither of these options blocks access to your site &mdash; it is up to search engines to honor your request.'=>'Cathetan: Ora ānā sijiā sākā opsi iki mblokir akses marang situs Sampéyan &mdash; iki kanggo mesin panggolekan kanggo ngregani panjalukan Sampéyan.','Attempt to notify any blogs linked to from the article'=>'Ngupāyāaké kanggo ménéhi ngerti sembarang blog sing disautaké marang artikel','Hi,
