tive plugin installationsLess Than 10'=>'Kurang Sākā 10','Trackbacks are a way to notify legacy blog systems that you&#8217;ve linked to them. If you link other WordPress sites, they&#8217;ll be notified automatically using <a href="%s">pingbacks</a>, no other action necessary.'=>'Trekbalik kuwi kanggo sistim péngetan blog resmi sing disautaké marang kabéh. Yén Sampéyan nyautaké situs WordPress liyā, kaé kabéh bakal diwārā-wārā otomatis nganggo <a href="%s">pingbalik</a>, ora perlu liyané manèh.','Excerpts are optional hand-crafted summaries of your content that can be used in your theme. <a href="%s">Learn more about manual excerpts</a>.'=>'Kutipan kuwi rangkuman coretan tangan opsional sākā konten Sampéyan sing bisa dienggo nang tema Sampéyan. <a href="%s">Sinau manéh ngenani kutipan manual</a>.','Active plugin installations1+ Million'=>'1+ Juta','You can edit the image while preserving the thumbnail. For example, you may wish to have a square thumbnail that displays just a section of the image.'=>'Sampéyan bisā nyunting gambar kanggo gambar mini. Contoné, Sampéyan  bisa nduwéni gambar mini persegi sing tampil namung nang seksi gambar.','Once you have made your selection, you can adjust it by entering the size in pixels. The minimum selection size is the thumbnail size as set in the Media settings.'=>'Sepisanan Sampéyan gawé kāyā sing dipilih, Sampéyan bisa ngepasaké kanthi ngisi ukuran nang piksel. Ukuran pilihan minimal kanggo gambar mini disetél nang setélan Media.','The checksum of the file (%1$s) does not match the expected checksum value (%2$s).'=>'Ceksum berkas (%1$s) ora cocog karo biji ceksum sing dikarepaké (%2$s).','%s has taken over and is currently editing.'=>'%s uwis dipindhahtanganaké lan saiki lagi disunting.','Thank you for Updating! Please visit the <a href="%s">Upgrade Network</a> page to update all your sites.'=>'Matur nuwun uwis ngupdate! Mānggā tiliki kācā <a href="%s">Upgrade Jaringan</a> kanggo ngupdate kabèh situs Sampéyan.','Image rotat